description:
X2ULink: Table recording X2U link information between eNodeBs.

dateTime: Timestamp of data recording.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Unknown identifier (likely redundant).
Id4: Composite identifier combining local and remote endpoints.
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format.
X2ULink.remoteEndPoint: IP address of the remote eNodeB endpoint.
X2ULink.x2ULinkId: Composite key uniquely identifying the X2U link.
X2ULink.localEndPoint: IP address of the local eNodeB endpoint.
